Justine Jones was left covered in huge sores after opening Tesco Finest Garnacha wine .
Mother-of-two had bought the bottle for granddaughter Abi's 18th birthday .
But despite the bottle being sealed and showing no evidence of being tampered with, the family were shocked when they found it contained a clear liquid which smelt of bleach .
Tesco said a report had been sent to their Technologist to investigate .